        pros:["Can capture complex non-linear patterns that statistical models miss","Handles multiple input features and multiple forecast horizons naturally","Temporal Fusion Transformer provides interpretable attention weights","State-of-the-art on complex forecasting problems with sufficient data"],
        cons:["Requires large amounts of data to train effectively","Much harder to set up and tune than statistical methods","Black box — difficult to understand why predictions are made","Overkill for simple patterns where ARIMA or ETS work fine"],
        what:"LSTM captures long-range temporal dependencies via gating. TFT adds multi-head attention for interpretable multi-horizon probabilistic forecasting at scale.",
