        cons:["Requires sufficient normal data to train on","Threshold for 'high reconstruction error' needs tuning","Deep learning overhead: GPUs, hyperparameter tuning, longer training","May reconstruct some anomalies well if they share patterns with normal data"],
        what:"Train an autoencoder on normal data only. High reconstruction error on new data flags anomalies — unusual patterns are harder to compress.",
